  "properties": {
    "encrypted": "false",
    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#### Simplifying with Annie\r\n\r\nAnnie got too excited and added a ton of duplicate blocks and <span style=\"padding: 2px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background-color: rgb(76, 86, 97); border: solid 2px #999; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 2px; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 2.5em;\"> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-waveform\" style=\"color: #F3DF55; margin-right: 2px\"></i> Effect </span> blocks to her song and now it doesn't sound very good. She needs help simplifying her code!\r\n\r\nUse **Abstraction** to focus just on <span style=\"padding: 2px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background-color: rgb(76, 86, 97); border: solid 2px #999; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 2px; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 2.5em;\"> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-drum\" style=\"color: #E565F5; margin-right: 2px\"></i> Beat </span>, <span style=\"padding: 2px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background-color: rgb(76, 86, 97); border: solid 2px #999; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 2px; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 2.5em;\"> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-boombox\" style=\"color: #58BEF9; margin-right: 2px\"></i> Bass </span>, and <span style=\"padding: 2px; font-size: 12px; color: white; background-color: rgb(76, 86, 97); border: solid 2px #999; border-radius: 5px; margin-right: 2px; white-space: nowrap; line-height: 2.5em;\"> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-guitars\" style=\"color: #64D25A; margin-right: 2px\"></i> Lead </span> tracks so it matches the example.\r\n\r\nYou only need to remove blocks from Annie's code to complete this level! You don't need to add anything new!\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/ccca247c75eb0ac57c2ac7009df869da-image-1742940511673.png)",
    "offer_browser_tts": "true",
    "use_secondary_finish_button": "false",
    "hide_share_and_remix": "true",
